Package: vorsph
Title: Spherical Voronoi
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Michael",
           family = "Sumner",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mdsumner@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Create a mesh of edges of Voronoi cells by triangulating points
 on the surface of a sphere and finding the dual. No spherical segmentizing is
 done, edge segments are purely linear in XYZ. 
